sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Operator
  participant Nexus as Archive-Nexus
  participant Logistics as Archive-Logistics
  participant Ledger as Archive-Ledger
  participant OS as ArchiveOS

  Operator->>Nexus: Generate synthetic logistics event
  Nexus->>Nexus: Store event in Nexus Outbox
  Nexus->>Nexus: Resolve target_service = LOGITICS
  Nexus->>Logistics: Publish event batch
  Logistics->>Logistics: Calculate route, ETA, delay risk, cost
  Logistics->>Logistics: Store logistics outbox event
  Logistics->>Ledger: Publish finalized logistics cost event
  Ledger->>Ledger: Create transaction and ledger_entry
  OS->>Nexus: Poll outbox summary
  OS->>Logistics: Poll operations and routes summary
  OS->>Ledger: Poll operations summary
  OS->>OS: Update ecosystem summary and topology

